DOCTORS SAY HIS SYMPTOMS ARE

22:07.993 --> 22:09.795
RELATED TO ACID REFLUX, A

22:09.795 --> 22:11.063
CONDITION THAT AFFECTS ONE IN

22:11.063 --> 22:12.431
FIVE U.S. ADULTS.

22:12.431 --> 22:14.266
NEW RESEARCH SHOWS GIRAFFES ARE

22:14.266 --> 22:15.334
SLOWLY HEADING TOWARD

22:15.334 --> 22:16.168
EXTINCTION.

22:16.168 --> 22:17.937
POACHING AND HUMAN POPULATION

22:17.937 --> 22:19.405
GROWTH HAVE REPORTEDLY REDUCED

22:19.405 --> 22:21.140
THE AFRICAN GIRAFFE POPULATION

22:21.140 --> 22:24.310
BY 40% OVER THE PAST 15 YEARS.

